    {
      "words": [
        {
          "w": "In this lesson we learn the numbers 3 to 10 with a masculine noun following them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "words": [
        {
          "w": "The word for \"one\" is وَاحِدٌ and it follows the noun as an adjective e.g."
        }
      ]
    },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "كِتَابٌ وَاحِدٌ" }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "One book" }] },
    {
      "words": [
        {
          "w": "The word for \"two\" is اِثْنَانِ and this also follows the noun as an adjective e.g."
        }
      ]
    },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "كِتَابَانِ اِثْنَانِ" }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "Two books" }] },
    {
      "words": [
        {
          "w": "But usually the word اِثْنَانِ is omitted because the dual form is enough to suggest the meaning of \"two\". But اِثْنَانِ is used for emphasis."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "words": [
        { "w": "Number 3 to 10: these numbers are used as mudâf, e.g." }
      ]
    },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "ثَلَاثَةُ كُتُبٍ" }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "Three books" }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "أَرْبَعَةُ بُيُوتٍ" }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "Four houses" }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "خَمْسَةُ أَقْلَامٍ" }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "Five pens" }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "عَشَرَةُ رِجَالٍ" }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "Ten men" }] },
    {
      "words": [
        {
          "w": "The noun that denotes the thing numbered  is called ma´dûd (مَعْلُوْدٌ)."
        }
      ]
    },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "خَرَجَ ثَلَاثَةُ طُلَّابٍ." }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "Three students went out." }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "فِي أَرْبَعَةِ بُيُوتٍ." }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "In four houses." }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "رَأَيْتُ خَمْسَةَ رِجَالٍ." }] },
    { "mode": "text", "words": [{ "w": "I saw five men." }] },
    {
      "words": [
        {
          "w": "Note: in كَمْ ثَمَنُ هَذَا؟ \"what is the price of this\" there is an omission. The word omitted is رِيَالًا or any other word denoting monetary unit."
        }
      ]
    },
